entry.title: Brazil's Lula Makes Remarkable Return to Power
entry.content: The 77-year-old standard-bearer of the Latin American left faces some of his toughest challenges yet, from uniting a divided nation to protecting the Amazon and boosting the incomes of the poor.

entry.title: Ukraine Begins 2023 Under Attack From Russian Drone Swarm
entry.content: Air-raid sirens sounded in Kyiv less than one hour after Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky delivered a New Year address just before midnight.
